xcfa (Powerful Audio Converter & Splitter for Linux)

XCFA is a tool to extract the contens of Audio-CDs and convert 
musical audio files conversion to FLAC, WAV, OGG, M4A, MPC, MP3, 
WavPack and many others.

Features:

 * Handling of frequency, track and bits.
 * Handling of files shared volume before a recording.
 * Web retrieval of Audio-CD information during treatment.
 * Small cover creation for Audio-CDs.

Optional dependencies:

 * cdrkit
 * faac 
 * faad2 
 * cd-discid
 * lame 
 * mac 
 * mp3check 
 * mp3gain 
 * musepack-tools 
 * shntool 
 * shorten 
 * vorbisgain 
 * lsdvd
 * aacplusenc
